inzelnen Segmenten des Tourismus tätig sind, vor- und dargestellt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aTourism. 4aGDS/CRS. 4aInternational Tourism Management. 4aTourismusarten. 4aTourismusformen. 4aTourismusmanagement. 4aTourismuspolitik. 4aTourismusverband. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  BWL, VWL 2013z9783110342659oZDB-23-OAV0 cprintz978348672506340uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348677991240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486779912423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486779912/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GBEc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OAVb2013